How to set up the environment and run the game:
*assuming that you have python installed on your computer already*

On Mac:

1.  place the "set" folder on your desktop
2.  Open up a terminal window
    -> this can be done by clicking on the "spotlight" and searching "terminal"
3.  type "cd Desktop" and click enter
4.  type "cd set" and click enter
5.  type "cd bin" and click enter
6.  type "source activate" and click enter
7.  type "cd .." and click enter
8.  type "cd src" and click enter
9.  Your environment is now set up!
10. Now, using the same terminal window (do not close it), type "python main.py"
    and click enter to run the game
11. You can now play the game!
